flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Detection of supply-demand imbalance or critical component shortage.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest supply-demand data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze global supply-demand imbalances using Cortex Auto Forecast.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Simulate mitigation options using AutoML.]
  N3 --> N4[PB: Process Builder - Execute coordinated actions through Process Builder.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle - Review outcomes and adjust strategies as needed.]
  N5 --> N6{Decision: Autonomous identification of bottlenecks and simulation of mitigation options.}
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS and improved on-time delivery.]
  N6 -->|Critical component shortage detected.| B1[Escalate and manage shortages using Process Builder.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Maintain production schedules and minimize COGS impact.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Emerging production bottleneck identi...| B2[Adjust production schedules and reallocate resources using Process Builder.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Maximize throughput and on-time delivery.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Unresolved capacity constraint.| B3[Initiate formal escalation process with predefined thresholds.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Take responsive actions to address critical constraints.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]